message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you this unique product that I believe will be of great value to you. After careful consideration, I'm willing to let it go for a price of $13500. This is a one-time offer, and I'm confident you won't find a deal like this anywhere else. Let me know if you're interested!
Hi Alice, thank you for your offer. However, $13500 is a bit out of my budget. I'm willing to pay $9000 for the product. Let me know if that works for you!

Hi Bob, thank you for your offer. I appreciate your interest in the product. However, I was thinking more along the lines of $11500. This is the lowest price I'm comfortable with, considering the product's value. Let me know if this works for you!
Hi Alice, I understand your position, but $11500 is still a bit high for me. I can go up to $9500. Let me know if we can meet in the middle!

Hi Bob, thank you for your revised offer. I appreciate your willingness to meet in the middle. However, I was thinking more along the lines of $10800. This is a compromise on my end, considering the product's value. Let me know if this works for you!
